  • Deprecated Interfaces 
    Interface and Description
    it.slyce.sdk.OnSlyceOpenListener
    as of Slyce SDK v5.1.0. Slyce.open(String, String, String, SlyceCompletionHandler) should be used instead.

    as of Slyce SDK v5.1.0. SlyceSessionListener should be used instead.

    as of 5.1.0

    as of Slyce SDK v5.1.0. Slyce.getDefaultSession() should be used instead.
    it.slyce.sdk.SlyceSearchRequest.Builder.filepath(Uri)
    This method is no longer functional. Please use SlyceSearchRequest.Builder.bitmap(Bitmap) instead.
    it.slyce.sdk.SlyceSearchRequest.getFilepath()
    This method is no longer functional. Please use SlyceSearchRequest.getBitmap() instead.

    as of Slyce SDK v5.1.0. SlyceScanner.getLensId() should be used instead.

    as of Slyce SDK v5.1.0 due to support for GDPR compliance. startSlyceActivity(Context, Slyce, String) or startSlyceActivity(Context, Slyce, List <String>) should be used instead.

    as of Slyce SDK v5.1.0. Please use Slyce.open(String, String, String, SlyceCompletionHandler) instead.
